branchCategory.name: C(D)A2*Q, Air Cylinder, Low Friction, Double Acting Single Rod
branchCategory.description: <p>Series CA2*Q is a low friction version of the light weight tie rod air cylinder.  Designed with low priston sliding resistance, this cylinder is ideal for applications such as contact pressure control. Low friction is in one direction only.  A variety of auto switches are available for mounting, including compact switches and magnetic field resistant switches.  The CA2 is available in 40, 50, 63, 80 and 100 bores sizes, and is RoHS compliant.</p>
